{"name":"Médaillon des pensées","permission":{"default":0,"YXEVHqx5k2ArOvJE":3},"type":"equipment","data":{"description":{"value":"<div>Le m&eacute;daillon a 3 charges. Tant que vous le portez, vous pouvez utiliser une action et d&eacute;penser une charge pour lancer&nbsp;<a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/grimoire/detection-des-pensees/\">d&eacute;tection des pens&eacute;es</a>&nbsp;(DD 13) par son interm&eacute;diaire. Chaque matin &agrave; l'aube, il r&eacute;cup&egrave;re 1d3 charges d&eacute;pens&eacute;es.</div>\n<div>Harmonisation requise.</div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Cadre de campagne","quantity":1,"weight":0.01,"price":3000,"attuned":false,"equipped":false,"rarity":"Peu courant","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":0,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":9,"long":0,"units":"m"},"uses":{"value":3,"max":3,"per":"charges"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"wis","dc":13,"scaling":"flat"},"armor":{"value":0,"type":"trinket","dex":0},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""},"strength":0,"stealth":false,"proficient":false,"attributes":{"spelldc":10}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/items/jewelry/amulet-blue.jpg","_id":"7oUBzKhfZg1RkjB0"}
{"name":"Bottes ailées","permission":{"default":0,"YXEVHqx5k2ArOvJE":3},"type":"equipment","data":{"description":{"value":"<div>\n<p>Tant que vous portez ces bottes aux pieds, vous disposez d'une vitesse de d&eacute;placement en vol &eacute;gale &agrave; votre vitesse au sol. Vous pouvez utiliser les bottes pour voler pendant un maximum de 4 heures d'affil&eacute;e ou lors de vols plus courts. Toutefois, chaque utilisation d&eacute;pense au minimum 1 minute de cette dur&eacute;e. Si vous volez au moment o&ugrave; cette dur&eacute;e prend fin, vous descendez &agrave; une vitesse de 9 m&egrave;tres par round jusqu'&agrave; toucher le sol.</p>\n<p>Les bottes r&eacute;cup&egrave;rent 2 heures de capacit&eacute; de vol pour chaque p&eacute;riode de 12 heures pass&eacute;es sans &ecirc;tre utilis&eacute;es.</p>\n<p>Harmonisation requise.</p>\n</div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Cadre de campagne","quantity":1,"weight":0.5,"price":8000,"attuned":false,"equipped":false,"rarity":"Peu courant","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"none","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":4,"units":"hour"},"target":{"value":null,"units":null,"type":"self"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":null,"per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":null,"type":"clothing","dex":null},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""},"strength":0,"stealth":false,"proficient":false,"attributes":{"spelldc":10}},"flags":{"core":{"sheetClass":""}},"img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/items/equipment/boots-plain.jpg","_id":"7yKXVugBT6HERl7v"}
