{"name":"Gemme élémentaire de feu","permission":{"default":0,"YXEVHqx5k2ArOvJE":3},"type":"consumable","data":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"description \">Cette gemme contient une particule d'&eacute;nergie &eacute;l&eacute;mentaire. Quand vous brisez la gemme par une action, un &eacute;l&eacute;mentaire appara&icirc;t, comme si vous l'aviez invoqu&eacute; avec un sort d'<a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/grimoire/invoquer-un-elementaire/\">invoquer un &eacute;l&eacute;mentaire</a>&nbsp;et la gemme perd toute magie. Le type d'&eacute;l&eacute;mentaire invoqu&eacute; d&eacute;pend de la gemme utilis&eacute;e.<br />\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Gemme</th>\n<th>&Eacute;l&eacute;mentaire invoqu&eacute;</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Saphir bleu</td>\n<td>&Eacute;l&eacute;mentaire de l'air</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Diamant jaune</td>\n<td>&Eacute;l&eacute;mentaire de la terre</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Corindon rouge</td>\n<td>&Eacute;l&eacute;mentaire du feu</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&Eacute;meraude</td>\n<td>&Eacute;l&eacute;mentaire de l'eau</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Cadre de campagne","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":960,"attuned":false,"equipped":false,"rarity":"Peu courant","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":0,"units":""},"target":{"value":10,"units":"m","type":"square"},"range":{"value":27,"long":0,"units":"m"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":1,"per":"charges","autoDestroy":true,"autoUse":true},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"consumableType":"trinket","attributes":{"spelldc":10}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/items/inventory/gem-red.jpg","_id":"9B4MALNxKUrUAs7C"}
