{"name":"Manuel d'exercices physiques","permission":{"default":0,"YXEVHqx5k2ArOvJE":3},"type":"consumable","data":{"description":{"value":"<div>Ce livre propose des exercices d'entretien musculaire, et ses mots sont chargés de magie. Si vous passez 48 heures sur une période de 6 jours au moins à étudier ce livre et appliquer ses conseils, votre valeur de Force augmente de 2, tout comme votre maximum pour cette valeur. Le manuel perd alors toute magie mais elle se recharge au bout d'un siècle.</div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Cadre de campagne","quantity":1,"weight":0.5,"price":100000,"attuned":false,"equipped":false,"rarity":"Très rare","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"hour","cost":48,"condition":"Passer 48 heures à l'étudier sur une période de 6 jours au moins."},"duration":{"value":0,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"units":null,"type":"self"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":1,"per":"charges","autoDestroy":true,"autoUse":false},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"consumableType":"trinket","attributes":{"spelldc":10}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/items/inventory/book-purple.jpg","_id":"XdpgXaPRu0WrSNob"}
{"name":"Baguette des secrets","permission":{"default":0,"YXEVHqx5k2ArOvJE":3},"type":"consumable","data":{"description":{"value":"<div>Cette baguette contient 3 charges. Avec cette baguette en main, vous pouvez utiliser une action pour dépenser 1 de ses charges et, si une porte secrète ou un piège est présent à 9 mètres ou moins de vous, la baguette se met à pulser et pointe dans la direction du plus proche de vous. La baguette récupère 1d3 charges dépensées chaque jour, à l'aube.</div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Cadre de campagne","quantity":1,"weight":0.5,"price":1500,"attuned":false,"equipped":false,"rarity":"Peu courante","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":30,"units":"","type":"radius"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":3,"max":3,"per":"charges","autoDestroy":false,"autoUse":true},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":"1d4 +1"},"formula":"1d3","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"consumableType":"wand","attributes":{"spelldc":10}},"flags":{"core":{"sheetClass":""}},"img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/items/weapons/staff-vine.jpg","_id":"XjT2Z6SooWd4FrhI"}
{"name":"Rapière Vengeresse sacrée","permission":{"default":0,"YXEVHqx5k2ArOvJE":3},"type":"weapon","data":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"description \">\n<p>Vous gagnez un bonus de +3 aux jets d'attaque et de d&eacute;g&acirc;ts avec cette arme magique. Quand vous touchez un fi&eacute;lon ou un mort-vivant avec, il subit 2d10 d&eacute;g&acirc;ts radiants suppl&eacute;mentaires.</p>\n<p>Tant que vous tenez l'arme en main, elle g&eacute;n&egrave;re une aura de 3 m&egrave;tres de rayon autour de vous. Vous et toutes les cr&eacute;atures amicales envers vous affect&eacute;es par l'aura obtenez l'<a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/utiliser-les-caracteristiques/#avantage-et-desavantage\">avantage</a>&nbsp;lors des jets de sauvegarde contre les sorts et autres effets magiques. Si vous poss&eacute;dez 17 niveaux ou plus dans la classe de paladin, le rayon de l'aura passe &agrave; 9 m&egrave;tres.</p>\n<p>Harmonisation requise avec un paladin.</p>\n</div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Cadre de campagne","quantity":1,"weight":1,"price":165000,"attuned":false,"equipped":false,"rarity":"Légendaire","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":0,"units":""},"target":{"value":0,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":1.5,"long":0,"units":"m"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"mwak","attackBonus":3,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["1d8 + @mod + 3","piercing"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"2d10","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":10},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"weaponType":"martialM","properties":{"amm":false,"hvy":false,"fin":true,"fir":false,"foc":false,"lgt":false,"lod":false,"rch":false,"rel":false,"ret":false,"spc":false,"thr":false,"two":false,"ver":false},"proficient":false,"attributes":{"spelldc":10}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/skills/light_05.jpg","_id":"XpU