{"name":"Potion d'amitié avec les animaux","permission":{"default":0,"YXEVHqx5k2ArOvJE":3},"type":"consumable","data":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"description \">Quand vous buvez cette potion, vous pouvez lancer le sort&nbsp;<a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/grimoire/amitie-avec-les-animaux/\">amitié avec les animaux</a>&nbsp;(DD 13) à volonté pendant 1 heure. Si on agite ce liquide trouble, on distingue de petits morceaux : une écaille de poisson, une langue de colibri, une griffe de chat ou des poils d'écureuil.</div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Cadre de campagne","quantity":1,"weight":0.1,"price":200,"attuned":false,"equipped":false,"rarity":"Peu courante","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"hour"},"target":{"value":1,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"touch"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":1,"per":"charges","autoDestroy":true,"autoUse":true},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"wis","dc":13,"scaling":"flat"},"consumableType":"potion","attributes":{"spelldc":10}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/items/potions/unique-4.jpg","_id":"bQgQpaMbP10cr2Pn"}
