{"name":"Épée longue ardente","permission":{"default":0,"YXEVHqx5k2ArOvJE":3},"type":"weapon","data":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"description \">\n<div>Vous pouvez utiliser une action bonus pour prononcer le mot de commande de cette &eacute;p&eacute;e magique et envelopper sa lame d'un linceul de flammes qui &eacute;mettent une vive lumi&egrave;re dans un rayon de 12 m&egrave;tres et une faible lumi&egrave;re dans un rayon de 12 m&egrave;tres de plus. Tant que l'&eacute;p&eacute;e est embras&eacute;e, elle inflige 2d6 d&eacute;g&acirc;ts de feu suppl&eacute;mentaire &agrave; toute cible qu'elle touche. Les flammes br&ucirc;lent jusqu'&agrave; ce que vous d&eacute;pensiez une action bonus pour prononcer de nouveau le mot de commande ou jusqu'&agrave; ce que vous l&acirc;chiez ou rengainiez l'&eacute;p&eacute;e.</div>\n<div>Harmonisation requise.</div>\n</div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Cadre de campagne","quantity":1,"weight":1.5,"price":5000,"attuned":false,"equipped":false,"rarity":"Rare","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":"Mot de commande."},"duration":{"value":0,"units":""},"target":{"value":0,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":1.5,"long":0,"units":"m"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"mwak","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["1d8 + @mod","slashing"]],"versatile":"1d10 + @mod"},"formula":"2d6","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":10},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"weaponType":"martialM","properties":{"amm":false,"hvy":false,"fin":false,"fir":false,"foc":false,"lgt":false,"lod":false,"rch":false,"rel":false,"ret":false,"spc":false,"thr":false,"two":false,"ver":true},"proficient":false,"attributes":{"spelldc":10}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/skills/fire_13.jpg","_id":"qSAzcmOsil67BDCI"}
