{"name":"Talisman de la sphère","permission":{"default":0,"YXEVHqx5k2ArOvJE":3},"type":"consumable","data":{"description":{"value":"<div>Lorsque vous effectuez un test d'Intelligence (Arcanes) pour contrôler une&nbsp;<a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/liste-objets-magiques/sphere-d-annihilation/\">sphère d'annihilation</a>&nbsp;en tenant ce talisman en main, vous doublez votre bonus de maîtrise pour ce test. En outre, lorsque vous commencez votre tour en contrôlant une&nbsp;<a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/liste-objets-magiques/sphere-d-annihilation/\">sphère d'annihilation</a>, vous pouvez utiliser une action pour la faire léviter sur une distance de 3 mètres plus 3 mètres supplémentaires × votre modificateur d'Intelligence.</div>\n<div>Harmonisation requise.</div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Cadre de campagne","quantity":1,"weight":0.1,"price":20000,"attuned":false,"equipped":false,"rarity":"Légendaire","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"units":"","type":"object"},"range":{"value":18,"long":null,"units":"m"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":"","autoDestroy":false,"autoUse":false},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"int","actionType":"abil","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["1d20 + @mod + @attributes.prof + @attributes.prof",""]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"consumableType":"trinket","attributes":{"spelldc":10},"details":{"description":"<p><em>Wondrous item, (requires attunement)</em></p>\n<p>When you make an Intelligence (Arcana) check to control a Sphere of Annihilation while you are holding this talisman, you double your proficiency bonus on the check. In addition, when you start your turn with control over a @Compendium[dnd5e.items.2YNqk5zm9jDTvd7q]{Sphere of Annihilation}, you can use an action to levitate it 10 feet plus a number of additional feet equal to 10